# FinTech Credit Risk & Loan Default Portfolio Engine

## Project Objective

Transform raw lending data into a structured PostgreSQL portfolio for credit risk analysis, borrower segmentation, and default monitoring.

---

## Table Creation

```sql
CREATE TABLE loan_portfolio (
    credit_policy INT,
    purpose VARCHAR(50),
    int_rate NUMERIC(6,4),
    installment NUMERIC(10,2),
    log_annual_inc NUMERIC(10,4),
    dti NUMERIC(6,2),
    fico INT,
    days_with_cr_line NUMERIC(12,4),
    revol_bal INT,
    revol_util NUMERIC(6,2),
    inq_last_6mths INT,
    delinq_2yrs INT,
    pub_rec INT,
    not_fully_paid INT
);
```

