## Data Quality Audit

### Duplicate Detection

```sql
WITH flagged_duplicate AS (
    SELECT *,
           ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
               PARTITION BY
                   credit_policy,
                   purpose,
                   int_rate,
                   installment,
                   log_annual_inc,
                   dti,
                   fico,
                   days_with_cr_line,
                   revol_bal,
                   revol_util,
                   inq_last_6mths,
                   delinq_2yrs,
                   pub_rec,
                   not_fully_paid
           ) AS row_num_dup
    FROM loan_portfolio
)

SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_flagged_duplicate
FROM flagged_duplicate
WHERE row_num_dup > 1;
```

### Key Insight

No duplicate records detected within the lending portfolio.

