## Outlier Detection

### Top Debt-to-Income Borrowers

```sql
WITH rank_debt AS (
    SELECT
        purpose,
        fico,
        dti,
        not_fully_paid,
        PERCENT_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY dti DESC) AS dti_percentile
    FROM loan_portfolio
)

SELECT
    purpose,
    fico,
    dti,
    not_fully_paid,
    ROUND(dti_percentile::NUMERIC,4) AS percentile
FROM rank_debt
WHERE dti_percentile <= 0.10
LIMIT 10;
```

### Key Insight

Borrowers with extreme DTI ratios represent the highest leverage risk segment.

