## Credit Risk Analysis

### Default Rate by FICO Score

```sql
WITH fico_group_metrics AS (
    SELECT
        fico,
        COUNT(*) AS total_loans,
        SUM(not_fully_paid) AS total_defaults,
        ROUND(AVG(not_fully_paid) * 100, 2)
            AS group_default_rate_percent
    FROM loan_portfolio
    GROUP BY fico
)

SELECT
    fico AS credit_score,
    total_loans,
    total_defaults,
    group_default_rate_percent,
    DENSE_RANK() OVER (
        ORDER BY group_default_rate_percent DESC
    ) AS default_risk_rank
FROM fico_group_metrics
ORDER BY group_default_rate_percent DESC;
```

